These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-1::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, whist, poker, backgammon
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, february, march
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, martial-arts, action, family
House: craftsman, victorian, tower, farmhouse
 1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
 3. the person playing scrabble is not the victorian house##6
 4. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 7. the person watching satire movies is the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is between the tower house and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 9. the craftsman house is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
10. the farmhouse house is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
11. the person playing whist is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
13. the person playing poker is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | poker     | scrabble      | backgammon      | whist    |
| Food          | april    | december | march | february     |
| Music-Genre   | family    | satire     | action    | martial-arts     |
| Nationality   | farmhouse | craftsman | tower    | victorian |

