.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, fisherman, teacher
City: miami, nizza, paris, london
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid, amaryllis, azalea
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, boat, tram, quad-bike
 1. the person driving the tram is the lawyer##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 3. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
 4. the person traveling to london is in an odd position##4
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
 6. the person traveling to miami is between the person who growsiris and the engineer##2
 7. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
10. the person driving the scooter is the person traveling to london##1
11. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
12. the person who growsiris is not the person driving the tram##6
13. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
14. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Food          | fisherman    | engineer | lawyer | teacher       |
| Hobby         | london | nizza   | miami  | paris       |
| Music-Genre   | azalea      | orchid   | amaryllis     | iris         |
| Sport         | scooter   | boat   | tram | quad-bike |

