 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the photographer##6
 5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
