 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
10. the photographer is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
13. the person traveling to liverpool is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
14. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

