 3. the person playing poker is on the left of the accountant##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is the person playing poker##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 7. the bolivar-smoker is the accountant##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the swisher-smoker##5
