11. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
12. the chaman-smoker is the chef##1
13. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
14. the chef is on the far right##1
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the accountant##6

.:: Answer ::.
