 2. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking milk is not the pall-mall-smoker##6
 4. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is the journalist##1
 6. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
 7. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the writer##3
 9. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
10. the person drinking sprite is not the ritmeester-smoker##6
11. the videographer is the videographer##1
12. the videographer is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person eating broccoli##2
13. the person eating broccoli is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | cucumber | broccoli     | peach    | spinach |
| Music-Genre   | fisherman | journalist       | videographer | writer    |
| Pet           | montecristo    | blend | ritmeester      | pall-mall |
| Transport     | lemonade     | sprite     | milk     | soy-milk |

