There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, soy-milk, water
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, billiard, whist
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, baking, sudoku, gardening
 1. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 3. the blend-smoker is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 4. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##5
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 9. the person playing billiard is not the blend-smoker##6
10. the blend-smoker is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6
11. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | bluemaster | oliveros  | ritmeester     | blend     |
| Movie-Genre   | soy-milk   | juice      | hot-chocolate   | water     |
| Nationality   | chess  | snooker   | billiard  | whist       |
| Transport     | baking   | collecting | sudoku | gardening |

 